high_descs: Turn around. Move to the wall. Then turn right and get to the coffeetable. Stand in front of the coffeetable.
Grab the fork.
Turn right. When you reach the gate, turn right. Exit the room. Go ahead and turn right. Continue to the microwave and stand in front of it. Bring up the bowl.
Open the cabinet. Take out the board, bowl, fork. Close the cabinet.
Turn right. When you reach the end, turn left. Go straight ahead and turn left as you enter the room. Continue to the bowl and turn left.
Turn right. When you reach the end, turn left. Go straight ahead and turn left as you enter the room. Continue to the coffeetable and turn left.
Place the board, bowl and fork on the left side of the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Find the fork, bowl, and place it on the coffee table.

high_descs: Head left  to reach the coffee table.
Pick up the fork on the left side of the coffee table.
Turn right and head down the passage on the right and head to the kitchen on the right to face the cabinet above the microwave.
Put the fork in the bowl.
Pick up the bowl from the cabinet.
Turn right and head left to walk to the end of the passage and turn left to reach the coffee table.
Put the bowl on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl with the fork on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the coffee table.
Take the fork from the coffee table.
Turn around and go near the bowl.
Put the fork into the bowl.
Take the bowl with fork from the table.
Turn around and go near the coffee table.
Put the bowl on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Placed the bowl on the coffee table.
